    "NER publications until August 2022 have reached 63 articles.NER topic articles were published in 134 journals, with the top ten journals shown in Figure 5.",
    "From 134 journals, 60% were in Q1, 30% were in Q2, and the remaining 9% were in Q3.",
    "Access became the journal that published the most articles about NER (32 titles), followed by the Journal of Biomedical Informatics (28 titles).",
